Cell.Text: I have heard news of this hunter arriving on our island, a man not unlike yourself, trying to disturb the humble people of Varghaven. | He was in search of a great beast, one of legend. I myself am not sure what became of him. I would suggest speaking with three people on the island. | Ursin: one of Varghaven's most skilled hunters, Geirbjorn: the general store owner, and Aelrica, the Karlsen Manor's Matriarch | From these three, I am certain you will reach some understanding of what became of the hunter you seek.

Node.Caption: _IGME_MCA_MainQuest_MeetingElder_AskAboutHunter: I've come to Varghaven seeking a missing hunter. What can you tell me about him?

Cell.Text: I do not keep track of the movements of every person who walks the island, outsider.

Node.Caption: _IGME_MCA_MainQuest_MeetingElder_MoreInfo: Do you not have any more information for me?

Cell.Text: Ursin can be found in the northern forests of Varghaven, Geirbjorn in the market square, and Aelrica is in the manor to the east of here.
[S] G|While I wish you luck on your quest outsider, see to it that you return to whence you came upon reaching its completion.
You will not bode well here, speaking as such.
G|I have nothing left to talk to you about.

That is most unfortunate, outsider. From what I hear, the islanders have not heard of him besides those three. | There is, however, one more person that might be worth talking to. Another outsider showed up at the same time as you did. A real shady fellow. | I do not know his name, but I've seen him loitering around the marketplace in a long hooded robe.

Node.Caption: _IGME_MCA_MainQuest_Elder_TheFenceTopic: I spoke with the three people you suggested. I still can't find the hunter.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Of course outsider, good luck on your quest.

Node.Caption: _IGME_MCA_MainQuest_Elder_FenceThanks: I don't know how useful that will be but thank you either way, elder.
